<p>
<br>
	<center>
	<p>This is a version of the famous boardgame <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Connect_Four">Connect Four</a> (<a href="https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vier_gewinnt">Vier gewinnt</a>) but played on the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Klein_bottle">Klein bottle</a> (<a href="https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kleinsche_Flasche">Kleinsche Flasche</a>).</p>
<p>The upper and lower boundary pieces of the game board are identified orientation preserving but the left and right boundary pieces are identified in such a way that the resulting surface is not orientable. More detailed rules and descriptions will follow.</p>
<p>Code by <a href="http://www.mi.uni-koeln.de/~heherrma/">Hendrik Herrmann</a></p>
	
